1
00:01:37,870 --> 00:01:40,990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:43,970
[Episode 26]

3
00:01:46,060 --> 00:01:50,380
[Xu Miyu]

4
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,160
If you insist on thanking me,

5
00:01:57,509 --> 00:01:58,259
how about

6
00:01:59,509 --> 00:02:00,910
we have dinner together?

7
00:02:12,770 --> 00:02:15,090
[Tonight]

8
00:02:25,020 --> 00:02:26,880
Do you have any plans for tonight?

9
00:02:26,950 --> 00:02:27,770
Come with me

10
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,820
to visit a restaurant.

11
00:02:28,820 --> 00:02:31,150
It sounds like
you're forcing her to work overtime.

12
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:32,240
You evil boss.

13
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,340
You scared me.

14
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,680
I also want to fully support your

15
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,280
hard-won spring.

16
00:02:39,590 --> 00:02:40,280
However,

17
00:02:40,810 --> 00:02:42,480
the winter of KPIs

18
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:43,740
is coming soon.

19
00:02:46,030 --> 00:02:47,820
The Golden Week has just ended,

20
00:02:48,030 --> 00:02:51,020
and there are still two months
before the summer vacation begins.

21
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:48,700
[Monthly Performance Report
of Purong Hotel]

22
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,950
[Monthly Performance Report
of Purong Hotel]

23
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:53,970
The rainy season is coming soon.

24
00:02:54,190 --> 00:02:55,560
The following days

25
00:02:56,420 --> 00:02:57,230
will be tough.

26
00:02:58,660 --> 00:02:58,980
[Monthly Performance Report
of Purong Hotel]

27
00:02:59,060 --> 00:03:01,410
[Statement of Expenditures]

28
00:03:01,410 --> 00:03:02,050
[Monthly Performance Report
of Purong Hotel]

29
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:10,800
Come on.

30
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:11,750
Back then,

31
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:13,560
we took a fancy to this building
at first sight.

32
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,510
It's the best one
in the entire residential compound.

33
00:03:15,510 --> 00:03:16,360
It really is.

34
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,500
Look.

35
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:19,550
The sunlight is great.

36
00:03:20,030 --> 00:03:20,560
As for the layout,

37
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:23,360
it has great ventilation
from north to south, too.

38
00:03:23,610 --> 00:03:25,070
In summer,
when we open the window just a bit,

39
00:03:25,070 --> 00:03:26,200
there will be a breeze

40
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:27,860
in the apartment constantly.

41
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,000
The decoration style of your home

42
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,190
is so classy.

43
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:32,840
This TV feature wall

44
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,030
looks so grand.

45
00:03:34,030 --> 00:03:34,560
Yes.

46
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,030
What material is it made of?

47
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:38,560
Fish Belly White Marble
imported from Italy.

48
00:03:38,590 --> 00:03:39,570
So beautiful!

49
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,329
Come and take a look.

50
00:03:42,329 --> 00:03:43,050
Come on.

51
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,050
Come over here.

52
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,840
They specifically hired someone

53
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,170
to design this nursery.

54
00:03:49,170 --> 00:03:50,930
You guys are so thoughtful.

55
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,970
The baby isn't even born yet,

56
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,170
but this whole room

57
00:03:55,170 --> 00:03:56,770
is already fully furnished.

58
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,910
As for this crib,

59
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:01,560
this brand is very expensive.

60
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,800
Sure.

61
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,970
It must cost tens of thousands of yuan.

62
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,800
My son and daughter-in-law

63
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,500
are both good at making money.

64
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:11,080
Not only are they willing to spend money
for my grandson,

65
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,080
but recently, they've also bought me

66
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,590
a new pair of presbyopic glasses.

67
00:04:13,590 --> 00:04:14,710
Touch and feel them.

68
00:04:14,710 --> 00:04:15,240
They're very light.

69
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:15,560
Yeah.

70
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,810
So light.

71
00:04:17,430 --> 00:04:19,390
When you wear them,
it feels like you're not wearing them.

72
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:20,810
They must be expensive.

73
00:04:21,269 --> 00:04:22,500
They just cost 18,000 yuan.

74
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:23,830
Mom, the price isn't 18,000 yuan.

75
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:24,830
It's 12,000 yuan.

76
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,360
That's right.

77
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,050
I have such a bad memory.

78
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:30,720
You're becoming such a humblebragger.

79
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,430
Just enjoy your happy life
with your son and grandchild.

80
00:04:32,430 --> 00:04:33,270
Right.

81
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:36,270
We won't just enjoy the benefits
without helping them.

82
00:04:36,270 --> 00:04:37,870
Since the children treat us so well,

83
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:38,870
as parents,

84
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:40,680
we should also
show our appreciation, right?

85
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,720
That's right.

86
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,920
My husband and I

87
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,210
have already discussed this.

88
00:04:44,210 --> 00:04:45,510
We'll pay for our daughter-in-law's

89
00:04:45,510 --> 00:04:46,510
postpartum care.

90
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,520
You are such a role model

91
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,270
as a mother-in-law.

92
00:04:50,270 --> 00:04:51,760
It's my duty.

93
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,380
It's time to eat!

94
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,360
Hurry up!

95
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,480
Let's eat.

96
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:56,690
It's time to eat.

97
00:04:59,630 --> 00:05:01,030
There are so many dishes.

98
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,080
Make yourselves at home.

99
00:05:03,510 --> 00:05:04,560
What a good wife and loving mother.

100
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,690
I wonder if it suits your taste.

101
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,560
Your daughter-in-law is so capable.

102
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,490
It's great.

103
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:12,680
Stop working.

104
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,380
Let's eat.

105
00:05:13,430 --> 00:05:14,460
The last dish.

106
00:05:15,430 --> 00:05:16,160
Remain seated.

107
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,070
I'll go help her.

108
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:18,370
Okay. Go ahead.

109
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:25,660
You guys...

110
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,920
You guys ordered takeout again?

111
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:30,120
You should have told me earlier.

112
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,880
I could have come
and prepared the meal for you in advance.

113
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:33,610
Mom,

114
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,120
you're out of date.

115
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,720
This restaurant is very popular.

116
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:38,970
It's authentic French cuisine.

117
00:05:38,970 --> 00:05:40,490
The most important thing is that

118
00:05:40,490 --> 00:05:41,320
she was

119
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:42,700
afraid that the delivery guy

120
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:43,870
would delay it,

121
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,220
so even during pregnancy,

122
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:46,370
she still went to the restaurant
to fetch the food.

123
00:05:46,370 --> 00:05:47,680
Don't you think that was so terrifying?

124
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:48,940
You have to be careful.

125
00:05:49,890 --> 00:05:51,220
Why are you saying this?

126
00:05:51,940 --> 00:05:52,670
Mom.

127
00:05:52,700 --> 00:05:53,990
When I'm done with this busy period,

128
00:05:53,990 --> 00:05:55,630
I'll personally make some fresh meals

129
00:05:55,630 --> 00:05:56,840
for Yucheng.

130
00:05:57,330 --> 00:05:57,980
Okay.

131
00:06:24,140 --> 00:06:25,430
[Summons from the People's Court
of Hongkou District, Shanghai]

132
00:06:25,530 --> 00:06:27,310
What's there to see?

133
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,390
What happened to you?

134
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:30,120
Why did you get the court summons?

135
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,240
What happened in the company before

136
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:31,800
has been solved.

137
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,240
It has nothing to do with me.

138
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,040
Come back.

139
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,900
I haven't finished speaking yet.

140
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:36,600
Well...

141
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,800
I noticed you didn't eat much today.

142
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,600
Are you hungry?

143
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,480
I'm not hungry. I have no appetite.

144
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:44,040
Do you think I'm annoying now?

145
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,159
No, I don't.

146
00:06:45,790 --> 00:06:47,480
Are you not feeling well?

147
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:49,920
How about going to the hospital
to see the doctor?

148
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,970
None of the questions you asked
was to the point.

149
00:06:51,970 --> 00:06:53,110
Are you doing this on purpose?

150
00:06:53,110 --> 00:06:53,550
I...

151
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,800
How am I doing this on purpose?

152
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:57,000
You know I've been under a lot of
pressure lately due to my company's KPIs,

153
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,460
but you just won't help me.

154
00:06:58,830 --> 00:06:59,830
The company's team building activity

155
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:01,390
isn't up to me alone,

156
00:07:01,390 --> 00:07:01,920
is it?

157
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,060
You always have excuses.

158
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:03,680
I just don't know

159
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,160
what the use of your position

160
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,410
as a vice president is,

161
00:07:06,410 --> 00:07:08,160
and what the use of marrying you is.

162
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:10,020
Let's not make a big deal out of it.

163
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:11,390
Alright.

164
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,040
I'll discuss it. Okay?

165
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,680
Not okay.

166
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,920
Not a single word you said is sincere.

167
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,580
You might as well say nothing.

168
00:07:23,390 --> 00:07:24,000
Fine.

169
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,360
I promise you.

170
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,360
About what?

171
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,040
About the team building contract.

172
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,600
What will you do
with the team building contract?

173
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,270
I'll let you
get the team building contract,

174
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:33,159
and it'll be held in Purong Hotel. Okay?

175
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:34,800
That's more like it.

176
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,720
You're happy now.

177
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:39,090
I feel like he's kicking me.

178
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:39,650
Alright.

179
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,600
Get some rest.

180
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,520
I'll go throw the trash away.

181
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,000
The door is unlocked.

182
00:07:55,350 --> 00:07:56,600
The door is locked.

183
00:08:05,340 --> 00:08:06,230
[Summons from the People's Court
of Hongkou District, Shanghai]

184
00:08:06,250 --> 00:08:07,490
[Case Cause: Marital Property Dispute]

185
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:09,040
[Summoned Party: Nie Yucheng]

186
00:08:27,630 --> 00:08:33,620
[Changyang Travel Company
—Corporate Team-Building]

187
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:28,800
Be careful.

188
00:08:28,870 --> 00:08:29,530
Be careful.

189
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,920
Lift it up a bit.

190
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,860
Okay. Alright.

191
00:08:33,940 --> 00:08:35,000
Move it a bit to the right.

192
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:38,770
[Changyang Travel Company
—Corporate Team-Building]

193
00:08:35,549 --> 00:08:36,750
Alright. Put it down.

194
00:08:37,909 --> 00:08:38,710
It's okay now.

195
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,720
-Thank you, Mr. Ji.
-Thank you.

196
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,650
You're welcome.

197
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,720
Mr. Ji.

198
00:08:44,940 --> 00:08:48,070
[Changyang Travel Company
—Corporate Team-Building]

199
00:08:53,330 --> 00:08:55,950
[Changyang Travel Company
—Corporate Team-Building]

200
00:08:59,490 --> 00:09:00,890
Do you need to avoid them?

201
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,650
No need.

202
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:04,830
I can handle the reception work.

203
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,240
Okay.

204
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:09,450
I'm right by your side anyway.

205
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:12,630
Thank you.

206
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,450
Okay. Thank you.

207
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:25,460
Mr. Nie.

208
00:09:26,180 --> 00:09:27,110
Nice to meet you.

209
00:09:27,550 --> 00:09:29,140
I'm Xue Rui,
assistant to the general manager.

210
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:30,510
Hello, Mr. Xue.

211
00:09:30,730 --> 00:09:31,450
Where is Mr. Ji?

212
00:09:31,450 --> 00:09:33,850
He's waiting for you
at the entrance of the banquet hall.

213
00:09:33,850 --> 00:09:34,540
Honey!

214
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,480
Mr. Xue.

215
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,820
I'll take my husband upstairs now.

216
00:09:38,820 --> 00:09:39,240
Okay.

217
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,790
Mr. Nie, this way please.

218
00:09:41,710 --> 00:09:42,840
I'm going upstairs.

219
00:09:45,010 --> 00:09:46,610
Give me your bag.

220
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,120
They're going upstairs.

221
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:57,550
Mr. Ji.

222
00:09:58,390 --> 00:09:58,910
Mr. Nie.

223
00:09:58,930 --> 00:10:00,240
-How have you been?
-How have you been?

224
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,150
Thank you for coming.

225
00:10:01,150 --> 00:10:02,150
Don't mention it.

226
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:03,270
You don't need to thank me.

227
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,720
You should be thanking her.

228
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,600
For this deal,

229
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,240
she badgered me every day.

230
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:09,050
She kept badgering me
even during pregnancy.

231
00:10:09,050 --> 00:10:10,360
This is my duty, isn't it?

232
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:10,840
Yes.

233
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,840
I just want to create profits
for the hotel.

234
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,320
That has always been
what I've been striving for.

235
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,360
Yes, yes, yes.

236
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:16,720
Come on. Let's go inside and talk.

237
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,120
Okay.

238
00:10:17,180 --> 00:10:17,870
Ms. Xu,

239
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,520
please show them the way.

240
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,400
Mr. Nie.

241
00:10:25,420 --> 00:10:26,450
Ms. Lu.

242
00:10:26,470 --> 00:10:27,500
If you need anything,

243
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:28,280
just let me know anytime.

244
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:28,890
Okay.

245
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:30,510
Please follow me.

246
00:10:35,510 --> 00:10:36,120
Let's go.

247
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:44,750
Please.

248
00:11:06,220 --> 00:11:07,360
Mr. and Mrs. Nie,

249
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,490
here are your seats.

250
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:12,040
Thank you.

251
00:11:12,410 --> 00:11:14,070
What are you thanking her for?

252
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,460
Bring us some chrysanthemum tea.

253
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,000
Ziyu.

254
00:11:19,650 --> 00:11:21,710
Mr. and Mrs. Nie
would like some chrysanthemum tea.

255
00:11:21,710 --> 00:11:22,560
Okay.

256
00:11:24,090 --> 00:11:25,360
If you two need anything else,

257
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,290
just let me know.

258
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,730
-Also bring me a cup of warm water.
-Ms. Lu, are you in the banquet hall?

259
00:11:28,730 --> 00:11:29,480
Yes, I am.

260
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:31,100
Just leave the banquet hall to me.

261
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:31,840
Ms. Lu,

262
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:34,240
please reconfirm this guest list.

263
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:42,480
Miyu.

264
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,360
There's an emergency in the kitchen.

265
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:45,090
They need you there right away.

266
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:47,870
Ask the receptionists to check

267
00:11:47,870 --> 00:11:48,600
this list of yours carefully.

268
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,840
There are definitely some mistakes.

269
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:50,320
Okay.

270
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:55,870
Mr. Gu.

271
00:11:55,870 --> 00:11:56,360
Hello, Mr. Gu.

272
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,270
Mr. Gu is here.

273
00:11:57,300 --> 00:11:58,560
Let's go greet him now.

274
00:11:59,690 --> 00:12:00,520
Mr. Gu.

275
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,000
Welcome.

276
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,480
Hello.

277
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:03,990
Come on. This way, please.

278
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:04,550
Come on.

279
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,600
Hello, Mr. Gu.

280
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,110
You're finally here.

281
00:12:08,110 --> 00:12:10,000
I even saw Mrs. Gu yesterday.

282
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:12,080
Come on. Please have a seat.

283
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:12,740
Have a seat.

284
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,510
Mom.

285
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:32,000
Why are you throwing a tantrum again?

286
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,600
Didn't we agree on this yesterday?

287
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,950
There's no performance
at the Jazz Bar tonight.

288
00:12:35,950 --> 00:12:37,090
It has been switched to the day shift.

289
00:12:37,090 --> 00:12:38,720
There are 300 people upstairs
having a team building activity.

290
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,840
If they all eat your boat pastries,

291
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,120
won't that be great advertising for you?

292
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:43,250
I'll make pastries for anyone but her.

293
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:48,280
Mom, who are you upset with now?

294
00:12:48,310 --> 00:12:50,130
It's all because of that Lu Zhenzhen.

295
00:12:50,130 --> 00:12:50,720
No wonder

296
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:53,290
she came to the restaurant
bossing people around early in the morning.

297
00:12:53,290 --> 00:12:55,620
It turns out
she's in charge of this order.

298
00:12:55,780 --> 00:12:58,180
I'm not taking the order
she's in charge of.

299
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:10,920
What are you doing?
Are you driving me away?

300
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,050
Mom.

301
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:15,000
Lu Zhenzhen has been Purong Hotel's

302
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:17,000
monthly sales champion
for six consecutive months.

303
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,090
Some of her clients

304
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,720
would stay at the hotel,

305
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:21,630
some would get gym memberships
at the Health Club,

306
00:13:21,630 --> 00:13:22,840
some would get massages here
all year round,

307
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:24,300
and some would often come here to eat.

308
00:13:24,300 --> 00:13:25,720
They are all over our entire hotel.

309
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:27,300
If you can't accept it,

310
00:13:27,330 --> 00:13:28,590
you might as well quit.

311
00:13:30,010 --> 00:13:31,720
I'm just losing my temper, aren't I?

312
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:32,720
Gosh.

313
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:35,950
You have no idea
how much I can't stand seeing her face.

314
00:13:35,950 --> 00:13:37,150
When I think about

315
00:13:37,170 --> 00:13:39,830
letting her eat such delicious pastries,

316
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:42,270
how I wish I could mix some sand in them.

317
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:42,910
Mom.

318
00:13:43,260 --> 00:13:45,630
Please don't talk nonsense
outside like this, okay?

319
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:47,200
If you don't
take your own specialty seriously,

320
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:48,350
you might as well quit.

321
00:13:48,350 --> 00:13:50,680
You're just ruining your own reputation.

322
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:53,360
I'm just losing my temper, aren't I?

323
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,360
Gosh.

324
00:13:54,420 --> 00:13:56,180
When I make the pastries later,

325
00:13:56,470 --> 00:13:57,520
I'll close my eyes.

326
00:13:57,520 --> 00:13:58,360
I won't look at

327
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,600
or listen to anything.

328
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,600
Is that okay?

329
00:14:01,230 --> 00:14:02,360
That's more like it.

330
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:04,950
Then later, just stay in the kitchen
and make pastries.

331
00:14:04,950 --> 00:14:06,460
Don't go anywhere. Okay?

332
00:14:07,380 --> 00:14:08,870
Okay?

333
00:14:10,060 --> 00:14:11,300
Okay.

334
00:14:13,570 --> 00:14:14,290
It's a deal.

335
00:14:28,700 --> 00:14:29,500
Isn't this...

336
00:14:30,530 --> 00:14:31,410
Miyu?

337
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:32,360
Hello, Mr. Hu.

338
00:14:32,900 --> 00:14:34,260
You're incredible.

339
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:36,240
Others get one year older every year,

340
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:38,000
but you're getting younger

341
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:40,080
and prettier.

342
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,910
Happy events bring good spirits.

343
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:43,480
Changyang is holding
such an important team-building event

344
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,870
in our hotel,

345
00:14:44,870 --> 00:14:46,240
which is the highest recognition of

346
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,840
the service quality of our hotel.

347
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:50,000
Of course I will present my best demeanor

348
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,660
to welcome all my old friends.

349
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,180
Come on. This way, please.

350
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:55,080
Mr. Hu.

351
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:56,870
I'm here to welcome you personally.

352
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:57,840
Mrs. Nie.

353
00:14:57,920 --> 00:14:59,000
-Please come in.
-Okay.

354
00:14:59,000 --> 00:14:59,510
Please.

355
00:15:03,630 --> 00:15:04,840
Here, Mr. Hu.

356
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:07,360
-Mr. Hu.
-Mr. Hu.

357
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,870
This way.

358
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:09,960
Mr. Hu.

359
00:15:10,340 --> 00:15:11,100
Nie.

360
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,520
You did a good job on this event.

361
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:14,610
I'm flattered.

362
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:15,490
Keep up the good work.

363
00:15:15,490 --> 00:15:16,360
Got it.

364
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:19,240
Why is there one set of tableware missing?
Waiter!

365
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:20,770
Come on. Please have a seat.

366
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:26,720
Miyu.

367
00:15:26,740 --> 00:15:27,680
Mr. Hu.

368
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,750
My wife

369
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:32,620
keeps talking about
your spiced beef every day.

370
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,410
As for her precious son,

371
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,480
if he doesn't
have your spiced beef for a day,

372
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,600
he just can't eat his meals properly.

373
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:39,100
It's very kind of you to say that.

374
00:15:39,100 --> 00:15:41,120
Actually, our Chinese restaurant has many

375
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:42,240
delicious dishes.

376
00:15:42,270 --> 00:15:44,120
If you have the chance,
you can bring your wife

377
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:46,250
and child here to taste them together.

378
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,000
Sure.

379
00:15:47,750 --> 00:15:50,210
I'll bring them here to dine
when I have time.

380
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:51,410
Please enjoy your meal first.

381
00:15:51,410 --> 00:15:53,210
Let me know if you need anything.

382
00:15:58,810 --> 00:15:59,630
Nie.

383
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:02,120
Did you see that?

384
00:16:02,520 --> 00:16:04,180
It's only been a few months
since you two broke up.

385
00:16:04,180 --> 00:16:06,140
Just see how much she has changed.

386
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:09,360
It's obvious
she has a bright future ahead.

387
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,510
When I walked up to her just now,

388
00:16:11,510 --> 00:16:12,510
I was really surprised.

389
00:16:12,510 --> 00:16:13,360
Mrs. Nie... No, no.

390
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:15,000
I mean, Miyu.

391
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,220
She has changed so much.

392
00:16:16,220 --> 00:16:17,120
You didn't see this just now.

393
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,870
When she gave instructions to the waiters,

394
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:20,750
she was so sharp-eyed and quick-witted.

395
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:22,840
She has the exact vibe
of a workplace elite.

396
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:26,720
Then it looks like getting divorced
isn't a bad thing after all.

397
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:29,730
Zhenzhen.

398
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:30,720
Are you speaking ill of me?

399
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,110
-No.
-No.

400
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:34,480
Today is your team-building day,

401
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:36,200
and this is my home turf, too.

402
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:37,630
We need to support each other.

403
00:16:37,630 --> 00:16:39,000
Absolutely, Zhenzhen.

404
00:16:38,940 --> 00:16:42,000
[Homecoming, Courteous Reception]

405
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:40,240
Alright.

406
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,510
Okay. I got it.

407
00:16:51,510 --> 00:16:53,110
Can I talk to you for a moment?

408
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:54,280
Mr. Nie.

409
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:56,540
I'm sorry but I'm very busy right now.

410
00:17:00,090 --> 00:17:01,690
Let's just talk for a moment.

411
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:06,579
I've received the court summons.

412
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:08,910
Is there any misunderstanding between us?

413
00:17:08,910 --> 00:17:10,310
We agreed on it when we got divorced.

414
00:17:10,310 --> 00:17:11,380
Why did you really sue me?

415
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:13,400
You concealed the marital property first.

416
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:15,160
I just took legal measures.

417
00:17:15,190 --> 00:17:16,670
You've misunderstood me.

418
00:17:16,790 --> 00:17:19,230
Honestly speaking,
I've given you everything that I could.

419
00:17:19,230 --> 00:17:20,720
That investment fund is already gone.

420
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:22,069
You know that clearly.

421
00:17:22,069 --> 00:17:25,069
Then where did you get the money
to buy a new apartment?

422
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,020
How did you find out about that?

423
00:17:29,020 --> 00:17:30,350
Did you investigate me?

424
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:32,240
If you don't want anyone to know,

425
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,970
just don't do it from the start.

426
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:36,640
Miyu, I don't think this is necessary
since we were once married.

427
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:38,200
Going to court would be embarrassing.

428
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:39,590
If you are short of money, just tell me.

429
00:17:39,590 --> 00:17:43,000
-I'll give you money.
-I just want to claim what is rightfully mine.

430
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:43,920
You weren't like this before.

431
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:45,200
What was I like before?

432
00:17:45,970 --> 00:17:46,700
Nie Yucheng.

433
00:17:47,030 --> 00:17:48,240
If you think I'm still that Xu Miyu

434
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:49,830
who can be bullied so easily,

435
00:17:49,830 --> 00:17:51,240
I have nothing to say to you.

436
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:52,240
See you in court.

437
00:17:52,240 --> 00:17:53,720
Well, I...

438
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:55,850
What do you mean by seeing him in court?

439
00:17:58,590 --> 00:17:59,990
Don't talk about it here.

440
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,190
Xu Miyu.

441
00:18:01,750 --> 00:18:02,980
Have you no shame at all?

442
00:18:02,980 --> 00:18:04,000
You've been divorced for so long,

443
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,480
and you're still asking your ex-husband
for money?

444
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:07,560
This is something
between Nie Yucheng and me.

445
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:09,090
It's none of your business.

446
00:18:09,820 --> 00:18:10,680
Let go!

447
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:11,700
I'm his wife.

448
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:15,170
Xu Miyu.

449
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:16,480
I'm warning you.

450
00:18:16,500 --> 00:18:18,740
If you dare to take this to court,

451
00:18:18,770 --> 00:18:21,830
I'll make sure
you can't make a living in this industry.

452
00:18:24,350 --> 00:18:25,240
You bad woman!

453
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:28,070
-Don't you dare touch my daughter!
-Mom, why are you here?

454
00:18:28,070 --> 00:18:29,510
Don't you dare give it a try!

455
00:18:29,510 --> 00:18:30,480
You wretched hag.

456
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:32,830
-Can you educate your daughter properly?
-What are you talking about?

457
00:18:32,830 --> 00:18:34,350
She's always acting like a beggar,

458
00:18:34,350 --> 00:18:35,000
asking for money everywhere.

459
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:35,640
Bah!

460
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:37,070
My daughter is asking for her own money.

461
00:18:37,070 --> 00:18:38,110
What does it have to do with you?

462
00:18:38,110 --> 00:18:38,830
Nie Yucheng!

463
00:18:38,830 --> 00:18:40,830
If you have any shame, don't play tricks.

464
00:18:40,830 --> 00:18:42,880
Just pay off your massive debt!

465
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:44,960
Otherwise,
regarding your cheating scandals,

466
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:47,000
I'll shout about them so loud
that the whole world will know.

467
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:47,750
-Mom,
-Believe it or not.

468
00:18:47,750 --> 00:18:48,880
Just shout then.

469
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:50,380
You'd better shout louder.

470
00:18:50,380 --> 00:18:51,960
Otherwise, I'll tell the police

471
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:53,400
how you and your husband

472
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:56,440
extorted my husband.

473
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:57,640
Let's see who will suffer more.

474
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:58,960
-Just tell the police then!
-Mom!

475
00:18:58,960 --> 00:19:00,480
Don't touch her.

476
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,960
Just tell the police if you dare!

477
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:02,720
Believe it or not...

478
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:03,720
Tell the police if you dare!

479
00:19:03,720 --> 00:19:04,920
Just tell the police!

480
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:06,440
Why did you hit her, Mom?

481
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:07,510
I'm not your mom!

482
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,440
You call her Mom?

483
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:27,520
Here, Mr. Nie.

484
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:29,160
Mr. Ji.

485
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:31,070
After all, Zhenzhen is pregnant.

486
00:19:31,070 --> 00:19:32,880
Doing this is certainly inappropriate.

487
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:34,310
-That's right.
-So I think whether...

488
00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:35,510
you can give us an explanation.

489
00:19:35,510 --> 00:19:35,720
Yes.

490
00:19:35,720 --> 00:19:38,440
You were the ones
who upset my daughter first.

491
00:19:38,440 --> 00:19:40,470
What kind of explanation do you want?

492
00:19:40,470 --> 00:19:43,070
Mr. and Mrs. Nie,
you've been treated unfairly.

493
00:19:43,070 --> 00:19:43,830
This matter

494
00:19:43,860 --> 00:19:45,860
is indeed my management failure

495
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:47,510
as the general manager.

496
00:19:48,270 --> 00:19:51,130
Please allow me
to sincerely apologize to you both.

497
00:19:56,870 --> 00:19:58,200
Mr. Nie, how about this?

498
00:19:58,240 --> 00:20:00,220
I'll arrange for Mrs. Nie
to go to the hospital

499
00:20:00,220 --> 00:20:01,270
for a checkup as soon as possible.

500
00:20:01,270 --> 00:20:02,730
All the expenses incurred

501
00:20:02,740 --> 00:20:04,500
will be covered by our hotel.

502
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:07,550
Mr. Ji.

503
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:08,510
Shouldn't these expenses

504
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:10,310
be covered by the two of them?

505
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:12,180
We can cover the expenses.

506
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:15,220
Ms. Xu is an employee of our hotel,

507
00:20:15,310 --> 00:20:17,620
and Chef Jiao is a cooperation consultant
of our hotel.

508
00:20:17,620 --> 00:20:20,480
Their matters should be
the responsibility of our hotel.

509
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:21,480
And we'll definitely do our best

510
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:23,550
to compensate you for your losses.

511
00:20:23,790 --> 00:20:24,720
But Ms. Lu,

512
00:20:25,290 --> 00:20:26,640
you are also an employee of our hotel.

513
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:28,640
You should know that this is a hotel,

514
00:20:29,130 --> 00:20:31,330
not a place to settle personal grudges.

515
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:33,400
So, please also respect

516
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:35,030
our hotel's principles
of handling matters.

517
00:20:35,030 --> 00:20:35,680
Mr. Ji.

518
00:20:35,950 --> 00:20:38,010
I don't care about personal grudges.

519
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:39,070
I am worried about the safety

520
00:20:39,070 --> 00:20:40,480
of the baby in my belly.

521
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:43,800
You can't treat me
so unfairly like this, huh?

522
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:50,030
Mr. Ji, do you think this...

523
00:20:50,030 --> 00:20:51,360
That's why I've told you

524
00:20:51,480 --> 00:20:53,550
to go to the hospital for a checkup
as soon as possible.

525
00:20:53,550 --> 00:20:55,480
We will take full responsibility.

526
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:58,640
Mr. Nie.

527
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:00,720
We've

528
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:02,980
always been good cooperative partners.

529
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:05,550
You probably don't want this matter

530
00:21:05,550 --> 00:21:07,480
to affect our future cooperation, either.

531
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:08,740
Please, for my sake...

532
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:09,880
Let's...

533
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:12,270
let this go.

534
00:21:22,200 --> 00:21:22,550
Okay.

535
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:33,550
Mr. Ji, I'm sorry.

536
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:36,670
My mother shouldn't have hit her.

537
00:21:37,030 --> 00:21:38,240
I failed to stop her,

538
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:41,210
so it's my responsibility, too.

539
00:21:41,210 --> 00:21:42,890
If you must punish someone,
just punish me.

540
00:21:42,890 --> 00:21:43,950
I'll accept it all.

541
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:48,060
It was indeed inappropriate
for your mother to hit her.

542
00:21:48,160 --> 00:21:49,510
But what I want to say is that

543
00:21:49,510 --> 00:21:50,770
you did nothing wrong,

544
00:21:51,270 --> 00:21:53,000
so you don't need to apologize.

545
00:21:57,480 --> 00:22:00,440
Today,
whether you're an employee or a guest,

546
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:03,140
first of all, you are a person.

547
00:22:04,790 --> 00:22:07,390
Letting others know you're not someone
who can be easily bullied

548
00:22:07,390 --> 00:22:09,380
is a right you should have.

549
00:22:39,680 --> 00:22:41,000
The door is locked.

550
00:22:55,310 --> 00:22:57,240
Here. Change into these slippers.

551
00:23:08,270 --> 00:23:10,200
If I hadn't found out about it
early today,

552
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:12,270
were you going to give her money
behind my back?

553
00:23:12,270 --> 00:23:14,800
You've got more money
than you can spend, huh?

554
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:16,480
I was just afraid you would worry,

555
00:23:16,480 --> 00:23:17,240
so I wanted to try reasoning

556
00:23:17,240 --> 00:23:18,190
with her first.

557
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:20,510
What's there to reason with her about?

558
00:23:20,510 --> 00:23:21,640
I won't allow you
to give our family's money

559
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:22,480
to that woman.

560
00:23:22,720 --> 00:23:26,270
Find the best lawyer to defend yourself
against her charges in court.

561
00:23:26,270 --> 00:23:27,480
Why do you keep squatting there?

562
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:28,370
Did you hear me?

563
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,880
I heard you.

564
00:23:30,550 --> 00:23:31,480
My stomach hurts.

565
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:32,680
Could you pour me a glass of hot water?

566
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:33,680
Your stomach never hurt

567
00:23:33,680 --> 00:23:35,030
until I started talking about
serious matters.

568
00:23:35,030 --> 00:23:36,230
Just endure the pain.

569
00:24:25,030 --> 00:24:27,240
Though that little vixen was so arrogant,

570
00:24:27,240 --> 00:24:29,900
I still got to slap her face hard today,
didn't I?

571
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:32,350
You saw how she looked today.

572
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:33,790
It helped to vent my anger,

573
00:24:33,790 --> 00:24:35,190
and it was so gratifying.

574
00:24:39,480 --> 00:24:40,720
Tell me the truth.

575
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:42,790
About what?

576
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:45,090
You and Mr. Ji...

577
00:24:45,270 --> 00:24:46,590
Mom, here you go again.

578
00:24:46,620 --> 00:24:48,160
Just calm down.

579
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:50,510
You always have this attitude
whenever I mention this matter.

580
00:24:50,510 --> 00:24:52,270
Because you always pair me off
with him arbitrarily.

581
00:24:52,270 --> 00:24:54,070
How am I doing that arbitrarily?

582
00:24:54,070 --> 00:24:55,310
Just think about what happened today.

583
00:24:55,310 --> 00:24:58,160
A general manager stood in front of you

584
00:24:58,160 --> 00:24:59,310
and apologized to that vixen

585
00:24:59,310 --> 00:25:01,060
so humbly.

586
00:25:01,270 --> 00:25:02,690
What did he mean?

587
00:25:02,790 --> 00:25:04,590
Even a blind person could see it.

588
00:25:06,400 --> 00:25:07,070
This matter

589
00:25:07,070 --> 00:25:09,240
is indeed my management failure

590
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:10,680
as the general manager.

591
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:14,160
Please allow me
to sincerely apologize to you both.

592
00:25:16,550 --> 00:25:17,440
In my opinion,

593
00:25:17,440 --> 00:25:18,240
isn't that little vixen

594
00:25:18,240 --> 00:25:20,640
just relying on the fact
that Nie Yucheng has a bit of ability?

595
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:22,790
That's why she can show off
in front of you.

596
00:25:22,790 --> 00:25:25,720
She even dared to complain it
to the general manager.

597
00:25:26,480 --> 00:25:28,310
Who does she think she is to do that?

598
00:25:28,310 --> 00:25:29,970
If you and Mr. Ji are together,

599
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:33,310
wouldn't you become her direct boss?

600
00:25:33,510 --> 00:25:34,480
By that time,

601
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:37,140
even Nie will have to fawn on you.

602
00:25:37,170 --> 00:25:38,200
Let's see

603
00:25:38,220 --> 00:25:41,150
if they would still dare to act wildly
in front of you.

604
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:42,780
But let me tell you.

605
00:25:42,920 --> 00:25:44,720
No matter what happens in the future,

606
00:25:44,720 --> 00:25:46,510
you can't be as impulsive as today.

607
00:25:46,510 --> 00:25:47,160
Okay?

608
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:48,240
Look at you.

609
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:49,500
What a little ingrate.

610
00:25:49,680 --> 00:25:51,880
I'm venting anger
and taking revenge for you.

611
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:53,310
I'm just afraid you'll get hurt.

612
00:25:53,310 --> 00:25:54,310
Besides,

613
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:56,560
isn't your daughter doing well now?

614
00:25:56,560 --> 00:25:58,240
Why do you always care so much about them?

615
00:25:58,240 --> 00:26:00,040
They bullied you so much before.

616
00:26:00,270 --> 00:26:01,750
Can you really forgive them?

617
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:02,940
Let me give you an example.

618
00:26:02,940 --> 00:26:04,750
For instance,
when you're walking on the street,

619
00:26:04,750 --> 00:26:05,750
a piece of chewing gum

620
00:26:05,750 --> 00:26:07,510
accidentally gets stuck to your shoe.

621
00:26:07,510 --> 00:26:09,230
You definitely want to get rid of it,

622
00:26:09,230 --> 00:26:09,920
right?

623
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:11,760
You just can't
fight with that chewing gum, right?

624
00:26:11,760 --> 00:26:12,400
Then...

625
00:26:12,920 --> 00:26:14,070
Then what if they do it again in the...

626
00:26:14,070 --> 00:26:16,470
If they dare to bully me again
in the future,

627
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:18,270
I just won't stand there obediently

628
00:26:18,270 --> 00:26:19,930
to let them hit me like before.

629
00:26:20,350 --> 00:26:21,080
Don't worry.

630
00:26:37,780 --> 00:26:38,720
[High Output Management]

631
00:26:38,930 --> 00:26:40,440
You're reading a management book, huh?

632
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:41,680
Mr. Tan.

633
00:26:43,550 --> 00:26:45,340
So you want to be a professional manager?

634
00:26:45,340 --> 00:26:47,270
I'm just setting a goal for myself.

635
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:48,880
Am I being too unrealistic?

636
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:50,750
No, it's good to have a dream.

637
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:51,480
However,

638
00:26:52,400 --> 00:26:54,060
being a professional manager

639
00:26:54,310 --> 00:26:55,370
is such a tough job.

640
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:56,880
Actually, you don't have to work so hard.

641
00:26:56,880 --> 00:26:58,000
No matter what you do,

642
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:59,440
you are just the best in my mind.

643
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:00,000
Really.

644
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:02,530
Are you leaving tonight?

645
00:27:02,530 --> 00:27:03,160
Yes.

646
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,160
The car will be here soon.

647
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:04,850
Oh, right.

648
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:06,750
Okay.

649
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:10,030
Then let me see you out.

650
00:27:10,030 --> 00:27:10,640
Okay.

651
00:27:11,030 --> 00:27:12,030
I can do it myself.

652
00:27:18,750 --> 00:27:19,510
Thanks.

653
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:21,850
Mr. Tan.

654
00:27:22,310 --> 00:27:23,640
I haven't had the chance to thank you

655
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:25,240
for what happened last time.

656
00:27:27,150 --> 00:27:28,950
Thank you for helping me so much.

657
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:31,750
And I was drunk last time.

658
00:27:31,750 --> 00:27:35,480
If I did something rude,

659
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:36,480
please forgive me.

660
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:37,160
No, no.

661
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:39,570
Actually, I was thoughtless last time,

662
00:27:39,600 --> 00:27:41,510
which caused you trouble.

663
00:27:41,510 --> 00:27:42,400
Of course not.

664
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:43,480
You helped me.

665
00:27:45,070 --> 00:27:47,150
I merely helped you out of a tight spot.

666
00:27:47,150 --> 00:27:48,680
If I really want to help you,

667
00:27:48,790 --> 00:27:50,920
I actually would like to take you away.

668
00:27:52,030 --> 00:27:52,510
Um,

669
00:27:52,530 --> 00:27:53,750
I mean,

670
00:27:54,270 --> 00:27:55,030
I-I know you

671
00:27:55,030 --> 00:27:56,160
really like your job here,

672
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:57,790
but the environment is still too tough.

673
00:27:57,790 --> 00:27:59,000
My company is also hiring.

674
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,260
Would you like to come?

675
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:06,750
Where are you
flying to this time, Mr. Tan?

676
00:28:06,930 --> 00:28:07,610
Hong Kong.

677
00:28:08,350 --> 00:28:10,120
I've moved my business to Hong Kong

678
00:28:10,120 --> 00:28:12,210
so that I can come here often.

679
00:28:13,250 --> 00:28:14,920
If you live closer to the old Mr. Tan,

680
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:15,920
it'll be convenient to take care of him.

681
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:17,450
And I can also see you often.

682
00:28:21,310 --> 00:28:22,310
The car is here.

683
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:25,880
Okay. Thanks.

684
00:28:29,970 --> 00:28:31,570
Take care. See you next time.

685
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:32,640
See you next time.

686
00:28:43,840 --> 00:28:44,880
No wonder

687
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:48,450
this girl doesn't
even like the general manager.

688
00:28:49,360 --> 00:28:51,090
So this is what's going on?

689
00:29:09,930 --> 00:29:11,340
Hello. This way.

690
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:12,240
Come on.

691
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:12,970
Give it to me.

692
00:29:16,790 --> 00:29:17,310
Here you are.

693
00:29:17,310 --> 00:29:18,390
Okay. Thank you.

694
00:29:18,420 --> 00:29:19,280
Please come in.

695
00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:26,120
This rainy season is so annoying.

696
00:30:03,390 --> 00:30:04,260
Honey.

697
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:06,900
This rainy season is so annoying.

698
00:30:06,900 --> 00:30:09,210
My shoes got wet after a few steps.

699
00:30:17,370 --> 00:30:18,720
A few days ago,
I noticed that Bottega Veneta

700
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:19,830
released a new pair of rain boots.

701
00:30:19,830 --> 00:30:20,750
They look pretty nice.

702
00:30:20,750 --> 00:30:21,750
I want to buy them.

703
00:30:27,630 --> 00:30:28,720
What are you busy with?

704
00:30:28,720 --> 00:30:31,320
Why aren't you
replying to my WeChat messages?

705
00:30:36,790 --> 00:30:37,720
It's damp.

706
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:38,480
Bake it again.

707
00:30:38,480 --> 00:30:39,420
If it's still not okay,
just throw it away.

708
00:30:39,420 --> 00:30:39,950
Alright.

709
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:43,640
Ya.

710
00:30:44,330 --> 00:30:46,050
Remind the warehouse that

711
00:30:46,080 --> 00:30:48,000
food easily gets moldy in this weather.

712
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:49,480
Ask them
to make sure to check the ingredients.

713
00:30:49,480 --> 00:30:50,000
Okay.

714
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:09,670
Hello, Mr. Ji.

715
00:31:09,670 --> 00:31:11,550
Here is the Red Bean and Coix Seed Water‌
you ordered.

716
00:31:11,550 --> 00:31:12,890
I'll hang a dehumidifier bag for you.

717
00:31:12,890 --> 00:31:13,440
Come in.

718
00:31:24,460 --> 00:31:25,460
Thank you.

719
00:31:31,940 --> 00:31:33,200
I think it tastes good.

720
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:36,600
Ask Chef Li to add a little
dried tangerine peel to it, too.

721
00:31:37,030 --> 00:31:39,500
This sweet soup
can help to remove dampness.

722
00:31:39,530 --> 00:31:40,420
We can offer it as a free gift

723
00:31:40,420 --> 00:31:42,380
to the guests
who check in during the rainy season.

724
00:31:42,380 --> 00:31:43,640
I think your idea is great.

725
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:44,700
I'll go arrange it now.

726
00:31:44,700 --> 00:31:45,190
Okay.

727
00:31:50,620 --> 00:31:53,890
[Purong Hotel
Performance Analysis Statistical Table]

728
00:31:53,990 --> 00:31:55,330
[The Purpose of the Activity]

729
00:32:06,080 --> 00:32:07,080
I'm sorry, Mr. Ji.

730
00:32:07,790 --> 00:32:08,750
Our chief editor said

731
00:32:08,750 --> 00:32:10,160
the rain in the suburbs was so heavy

732
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:11,960
that he couldn't make it by noon.

733
00:32:12,670 --> 00:32:14,000
Then what about dinner?

734
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:15,200
It's not very safe

735
00:32:15,720 --> 00:32:16,920
to travel at night.

736
00:32:16,920 --> 00:32:17,580
Besides,

737
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:18,680
our chief editor

738
00:32:18,680 --> 00:32:22,200
has already checked into
the InterContinental Hotel over there.

739
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:23,200
It's getting late.

740
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:24,440
We should take our leave.

741
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:24,880
Okay.

742
00:32:26,900 --> 00:32:27,720
Mr. Ji,

743
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:29,480
the price we just mentioned

744
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:31,690
is already the highest one we can offer.

745
00:32:31,720 --> 00:32:32,630
Mr. Ji, please

746
00:32:32,750 --> 00:32:33,950
think about it again.

747
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:34,680
Okay.

748
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:36,460
We will think about it seriously.

749
00:32:36,460 --> 00:32:37,030
Okay.

750
00:32:37,050 --> 00:32:37,910
I'll leave now.

751
00:32:38,750 --> 00:32:40,280
Okay. Let me see you all out.

752
00:32:45,240 --> 00:32:47,700
Should we
talk to their deputy editor again?

753
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,400
What they originally wanted

754
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:52,200
were two venues,
one indoor and one outdoor,

755
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:53,480
which complemented each other.

756
00:32:53,480 --> 00:32:55,140
But now with the rainy season,

757
00:32:55,310 --> 00:32:57,070
the garden terrace cannot be used.

758
00:32:57,070 --> 00:32:58,720
It's not surprising
that they want a lower price.

759
00:32:58,720 --> 00:33:01,240
We've already offered them
the lowest price.

760
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:02,640
If we accept the price they offered,

761
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:04,770
we will definitely lose money on this.

762
00:33:09,180 --> 00:33:13,440
[Purong Hotel]

763
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:13,240
Mr. Ji.

764
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:15,000
You must have stayed

765
00:33:15,000 --> 00:33:16,930
in the deserts abroad for too long.

766
00:33:17,050 --> 00:33:18,000
Have you forgotten

767
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:20,750
the most annoying thing
about Shanghai is this rainy season?

768
00:33:20,750 --> 00:33:21,510
Now look.

769
00:33:22,070 --> 00:33:22,920
Without a backup plan,

770
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:24,720
our business is badly affected.

771
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:25,880
Mr. Ji.

772
00:33:26,270 --> 00:33:26,790
Don't forget that

773
00:33:26,790 --> 00:33:29,390
we have a VAM agreement
hanging over our heads.

774
00:33:29,480 --> 00:33:31,140
What do you think we should do?

775
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:36,240
Thank you for reminding me, Mr. Wei.

776
00:33:36,620 --> 00:33:38,080
I did stay in the desert regions

777
00:33:38,080 --> 00:33:39,270
of the Middle East and North Africa

778
00:33:39,270 --> 00:33:40,960
for a period of time.

779
00:33:41,550 --> 00:33:43,680
And I interacted a lot with the locals.

780
00:33:44,130 --> 00:33:45,060
Those residents

781
00:33:45,550 --> 00:33:47,640
in the tropical desert climate zone

782
00:33:47,640 --> 00:33:50,170
are very passionate
about watching the rain.

783
00:33:50,270 --> 00:33:51,200
Our off-season

784
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:53,640
might just be their peak season.

785
00:33:55,590 --> 00:33:57,070
Did you all hear that?

786
00:33:57,640 --> 00:33:58,700
Watching the rain?

787
00:33:59,340 --> 00:34:00,900
Are you joking with us?

788
00:34:00,930 --> 00:34:01,810
Mr. Ji.

789
00:34:02,380 --> 00:34:03,440
Elaborate on that.

790
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:04,920
Okay.

791
00:34:07,870 --> 00:34:09,070
[North Africa Rain Viewing Group Planning]

792
00:34:09,199 --> 00:34:10,280
Currently, we've established

793
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:13,540
partnerships with eight travel agencies
in North Africa.

794
00:34:13,550 --> 00:34:15,230
This year, they will open up

795
00:34:15,230 --> 00:34:17,190
a new route
for watching rain in East Asia.

796
00:34:17,190 --> 00:34:19,449
From this week until the end of the month,

797
00:34:19,449 --> 00:34:20,320
these rain-viewing groups

798
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:22,800
will check into
our Purong Hotel successively.

799
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:24,550
That's just a drop in the bucket.

800
00:34:24,550 --> 00:34:26,800
Even if your so-called rain-viewing groups

801
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,510
stay at our hotel,

802
00:34:27,510 --> 00:34:29,080
can they fill up all the guest rooms?

803
00:34:29,080 --> 00:34:30,800
And what should we do after they leave?

804
00:34:30,800 --> 00:34:34,510
Shall we find
cloud-viewing or star-viewing groups next?

805
00:34:34,610 --> 00:34:36,130
It's a temporary expedient indeed.

806
00:34:36,130 --> 00:34:37,040
But at least,

807
00:34:37,070 --> 00:34:39,400
it can increase the occupancy rate by 30%.

808
00:34:40,100 --> 00:34:41,710
Mr. Wei, do you have a way

809
00:34:41,730 --> 00:34:43,030
to solve this issue once and for all?

810
00:34:43,030 --> 00:34:45,480
You might as well bring it up
and discuss it with us all.

811
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:45,960
I...

812
00:34:48,030 --> 00:34:48,710
Alright.

813
00:34:49,550 --> 00:34:51,880
Let's follow Mr. Ji's plan for now.

814
00:34:52,630 --> 00:34:53,230
Okay.

815
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,190
-Welcome.
-Thank you.

816
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:01,800
Welcome.

817
00:35:10,830 --> 00:35:14,010
Human joys and sorrows
are not mutually comprehensible.

818
00:35:14,010 --> 00:35:16,550
Some people would travel miles
to watch the rain,

819
00:35:16,550 --> 00:35:18,880
while some would get annoyed at the sight

820
00:35:18,880 --> 00:35:20,140
of this humid weather.

821
00:35:20,280 --> 00:35:22,740
Having business
is better than having none.

822
00:35:23,320 --> 00:35:26,070
The rain-viewing groups
can only help temporarily, not forever.

823
00:35:26,070 --> 00:35:27,070
Just wait and see.

824
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:28,960
When this trend passes,

825
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:30,960
we'll be back to the original state.

826
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:35,110
Hello.

827
00:35:35,110 --> 00:35:36,770
Purong Hotel at your service.

828
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:40,710
You'll check in on the night of June 6th

829
00:35:40,710 --> 00:35:42,800
and check out on the 10th. Is that right?

830
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:44,530
A standard double room, right?

831
00:35:44,630 --> 00:35:45,920
Yes, we have standard double rooms.

832
00:35:45,920 --> 00:35:47,980
May I have your phone number, please?

833
00:35:48,190 --> 00:35:48,960
Ask the guest

834
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:50,690
if he has any special requests.

835
00:35:51,370 --> 00:35:54,230
Do you have any specific requirements
for the room?

836
00:35:55,230 --> 00:35:56,820
You want a higher floor.

837
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:58,400
You want it to be quiet.

838
00:36:00,480 --> 00:36:01,190
Don't worry.

839
00:36:01,190 --> 00:36:02,920
The soundproofing effect
in our hotel is excellent.

840
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:04,400
Okay. We look forward to your visit.

841
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:05,330
Goodbye, Ma'am.

842
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:08,110
Lu Xiaoyan.

843
00:36:09,050 --> 00:36:10,230
Did you also receive bookings yesterday

844
00:36:10,230 --> 00:36:12,230
for June 6th to 9th?

845
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:15,360
I think so.

846
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:16,670
Check it right now.

847
00:36:18,510 --> 00:36:19,110
Okay.

848
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:21,320
I found it.

849
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:22,190
There is such a booking.

850
00:36:22,190 --> 00:36:23,280
The reservation is

851
00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:25,130
from the 6th to the 9th of next month.

852
00:36:25,130 --> 00:36:26,370
Please check again to see

853
00:36:26,370 --> 00:36:27,400
whether there are other bookings

854
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:28,590
during this period.

855
00:36:28,670 --> 00:36:30,070
Why are we checking this?

856
00:36:30,840 --> 00:36:31,510
Yes.

857
00:36:34,180 --> 00:36:35,960
I found five bookings in total.

858
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:38,070
Four of them are from the 6th to the 9th,

859
00:36:38,070 --> 00:36:40,880
and one is from the 6th to the 10th.

860
00:36:43,840 --> 00:36:46,320
We also need to
inform the colleagues on other shifts

861
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:47,230
about this.

862
00:36:47,230 --> 00:36:49,510
Any bookings between the 6th and the 9th

863
00:36:49,510 --> 00:36:51,840
or the 10th of next month

864
00:36:51,840 --> 00:36:53,400
should be marked with notes.

865
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:54,990
Then send the information
to Shi Huanhuan for summaries.

866
00:36:54,990 --> 00:36:56,230
You're in charge of recording it

867
00:36:56,230 --> 00:36:57,640
and giving it to me every day. Okay?

868
00:36:57,640 --> 00:36:58,190
Okay.

869
00:36:58,320 --> 00:36:59,230
Ms. Xu,

870
00:36:59,550 --> 00:37:00,900
why is that?

871
00:37:01,050 --> 00:37:02,270
Think about it.

872
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:03,030
Every year,

873
00:37:03,030 --> 00:37:05,320
what days are June 7th to 10th?

874
00:37:07,110 --> 00:37:08,230
-The college entrance exam!
-The college entrance exam!

875
00:37:08,230 --> 00:37:10,280
But the graded exam
for the three elective subjects

876
00:37:10,280 --> 00:37:12,190
was already taken last week, wasn't it?

877
00:37:12,190 --> 00:37:13,400
So we just can't miss the exam

878
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:14,660
for the three compulsory subjects.

879
00:37:14,660 --> 00:37:17,070
Since the bookings
have given us enough hints,

880
00:37:17,070 --> 00:37:18,870
we can't miss this opportunity.

881
00:37:19,190 --> 00:37:20,310
But

882
00:37:20,510 --> 00:37:22,040
what if it's a coincidence?

883
00:37:22,110 --> 00:37:24,400
Our Purong Hotel is a five-star hotel.

884
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:25,550
Staying in our hotel for a day,

885
00:37:25,550 --> 00:37:28,280
with meals and accommodation,
would cost over 1,000 yuan, right?

886
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:30,800
How many college entrance exam-takers'
families can afford that?

887
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:31,880
Besides,

888
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:34,760
who knows if there's an exam site nearby?

889
00:37:35,520 --> 00:37:36,920
Whether it's a coincidence
or an opportunity,

890
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:39,040
we need to find out
before we discuss further.

891
00:37:39,040 --> 00:37:39,840
In our area,

892
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:40,920
the "3+3" new pattern

893
00:37:40,920 --> 00:37:42,920
of the college entrance exam
has been implemented for years.

894
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:44,510
As for the quantity and locations

895
00:37:44,510 --> 00:37:46,110
of the exam sites each year,

896
00:37:46,110 --> 00:37:47,560
we should investigate them clearly.

897
00:37:47,560 --> 00:37:49,280
Hotels belong to the service industry.

898
00:37:49,280 --> 00:37:50,110
We can't just wait

899
00:37:50,110 --> 00:37:51,880
for guests to initiatively come to us.

900
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:53,400
We need to take the initiative to discover

901
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:54,360
the guests' needs

902
00:37:54,360 --> 00:37:56,160
and provide them with the best service.

903
00:37:56,160 --> 00:37:58,670
Only in this way can we stand out

904
00:37:58,670 --> 00:38:00,200
in the fierce competition.

905
00:38:00,360 --> 00:38:01,070
Got it?

906
00:38:01,230 --> 00:38:02,000
Understood.

907
00:38:02,510 --> 00:38:03,510
Let's get to work.

908
00:38:15,930 --> 00:38:16,550
What are you looking at

909
00:38:16,550 --> 00:38:17,400
so seriously?

910
00:38:17,580 --> 00:38:20,240
The college entrance exam sites
near our hotel.

911
00:38:21,690 --> 00:38:22,760
Since when have you been so obedient

912
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:24,220
to Ms. Xu's instructions?

913
00:38:25,190 --> 00:38:27,920
I'm not being obedient
to Ms. Xu's instructions.

914
00:38:27,920 --> 00:38:30,110
My cousin will take
the college entrance exam this year.

915
00:38:30,110 --> 00:38:31,070
I'm just curious,

916
00:38:31,070 --> 00:38:32,730
so I'm looking it up casually.

917
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:35,790
In my opinion,

918
00:38:35,820 --> 00:38:37,640
when it comes to the tasks
of getting clients,

919
00:38:37,640 --> 00:38:39,760
there should be some news
coming from the marketing

920
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:41,670
and sales departments first, right?

921
00:38:41,670 --> 00:38:43,400
You and I are so well-informed,

922
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:44,760
but we still don't know anything about it.

923
00:38:44,760 --> 00:38:46,360
It must be totally baseless.

924
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:47,320
Ms. Xu really

925
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:49,450
knows how to make trouble for herself.

926
00:38:49,920 --> 00:38:51,500
She's not making trouble for you.

927
00:38:51,500 --> 00:38:53,030
Why are you talking so much?

928
00:38:54,120 --> 00:38:55,040
Hurry up and eat.

929
00:38:55,040 --> 00:38:57,240
We have to change shifts after the meal.

930
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:05,800
Ms. Xu,

931
00:39:05,820 --> 00:39:06,670
instead of having a meal,

932
00:39:06,670 --> 00:39:08,110
what are you busy with here?

933
00:39:08,110 --> 00:39:09,710
I'm doing a little research.

934
00:39:10,180 --> 00:39:12,160
Why are you circling
so many spots in red ink?

935
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:13,400
Are you going to buy a house?

936
00:39:13,400 --> 00:39:14,710
No.

937
00:39:14,710 --> 00:39:17,280
I'm just checking where these
college entrance exam sites are.

938
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:18,480
I'd like to see if there are any of them

939
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:19,400
near our hotel.

940
00:39:20,190 --> 00:39:21,520
Don't bother with this.

941
00:39:21,710 --> 00:39:22,840
No college entrance exam sites

942
00:39:22,840 --> 00:39:24,670
have ever been set up near our hotel.

943
00:39:24,670 --> 00:39:27,130
Those exam-takers rarely
stay in our hotel.

944
00:39:27,510 --> 00:39:28,770
I'll get going, Ma'am.

945
00:39:36,690 --> 00:39:37,240
[Fuxing High School
Affiliated to Fudan University] [2.5 km]

946
00:39:37,270 --> 00:39:38,410
[The Affiliated High School
of East China Normal University] [1.5 km]

947
00:39:38,440 --> 00:39:39,710
[Xinhua Finance and Economics School]

948
00:39:59,510 --> 00:40:00,760
You're at home, huh?

949
00:40:01,850 --> 00:40:04,110
Why didn't you turn on the lights at home?

950
00:40:04,590 --> 00:40:07,050
You also didn't reply
to my WeChat messages.

951
00:40:10,030 --> 00:40:11,830
Why aren't you saying anything?

952
00:40:13,740 --> 00:40:15,870
You didn't close that window, either.

953
00:40:16,230 --> 00:40:17,000
It's so damp inside.

954
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:19,260
Why didn't you turn on the dehumidifier?

955
00:40:32,890 --> 00:40:34,360
What's wrong with me
buying a pair of boots?

956
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:36,070
I have to
carry such a big belly every day,

957
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:37,230
and it's so heavy.

958
00:40:39,880 --> 00:40:41,080
The doctor told me...

959
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:44,370
to go to the hospital tomorrow

960
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:48,290
for an enhanced abdominal CT scan.

961
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:52,320
Can you go with me?

962
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:01,510
What's wrong?
